TITLE: Creating New Quasar Project with Package Managers
DESCRIPTION: Commands to create a new Quasar project using different package managers including Yarn, NPM, PNPM, and Bun (experimental).
SOURCE: https://github.com/quasarframework/quasar.git/blob/dev/docs/src/pages/start/quick-start.md#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
$ yarn create quasar
$ npm init quasar@latest
$ pnpm create quasar@latest
# experimental support
$ bun create quasar@latest
```

