TITLE: Implementing a Counter Store with Pinia
DESCRIPTION: Creates a counter store implementation using Pinia. The store defines state (counter), getters (doubleCount), and actions (increment).
SOURCE: https://github.com/quasarframework/quasar.git/blob/dev/docs/src/pages/quasar-cli-webpack/state-management-with-pinia.md#2025-04-16_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import { defineStore } from 'pinia'

export const useCounterStore = defineStore('counter', {
  state: () => ({
    counter: 0,
  }),
  getters: {
    doubleCount: (state) => state.counter * 2,
  },
  actions: {
    increment() {
      this.counter++;
    },
  },
})
```

