TITLE: Implementing Authentication Guards with Vue Router and Pinia in Quasar
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to use Vue Router's beforeEach guard to check authentication status using a Pinia store in a Quasar application. It redirects unauthenticated users trying to access protected routes to a signin page while preserving the originally requested path in the query parameters.
SOURCE: https://github.com/quasarframework/quasar.git/blob/dev/docs/src/pages/quasar-cli-webpack/routing.md#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
export default function ({ store /*, ssrContext */ }) {
  // ...
  const userStore = useUserStore(store)

  Router.beforeEach((to, from, next) => {
