TITLE: Configuring Browser DevTools Access in Electron Main Process
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of conditional DevTools access in an Electron app. Opens DevTools automatically in debug mode and prevents access in production. Uses the createWindow function to manage BrowserWindow instance behavior.
SOURCE: https://github.com/quasarframework/quasar.git/blob/dev/docs/src/pages/quasar-cli-webpack/developing-electron-apps/troubleshooting-and-tips.md#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
function createWindow () {
  mainWindow = new BrowserWindow({ ... })

  if (process.env.DEBUGGING) {
    // if on DEV or Production with debug enabled
    mainWindow.webContents.openDevTools()
  }
  else {
    // we're on production; no access to devtools pls
    mainWindow.webContents.on('devtools-opened', () => {
      mainWindow.webContents.closeDevTools()
    })
  }
}
```

