TITLE: Implementing PreFetch in Vue Component
DESCRIPTION: Example of a Vue component with PreFetch hook implementation using Pinia store
SOURCE: https://github.com/quasarframework/quasar.git/blob/dev/docs/src/pages/quasar-cli-vite/prefetch-feature.md#2025-04-16_snippet_2

