TITLE: Implementing File Upload with Perl Mojolicious
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to implement a file upload endpoint using Perl Mojolicious framework. It includes CORS configuration and a route for handling file uploads.
SOURCE: https://github.com/quasarframework/quasar.git/blob/dev/docs/src/pages/vue-components/uploader.md#2025-04-16_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: perl
CODE:
```
use Mojolicious::Lite -signatures;

# CORS
app->hook(after_dispatch => sub {
    my $c = shift;
    $c->res->headers->header('Access-Control-Allow-Origin' => '*');
});
options '*' => sub ($c) {
   $c->res->headers->header('Access-Control-Allow-Methods' => 'GET, OPTIONS, POST, DELETE, PUT');
   $c->res->headers->header('Access-Control-Allow-Headers' => 'Content-Type');
   $c->render(text => '');
};

post '/upload' => sub ($c) {
   my $uploads = $c->req->uploads('files');

   foreach my $f (@{$uploads}) {
      $f->move_to('/tmp/' . $f->filename);
   }

   $c->render(text => 'Saved!');
};

app->start;
```

